name: Sybesque - Sybase database browser
short_description: Sybesque is a GUI for browsing Sybase databases. It will display table, stored procedure and trigger definitions. Stored procedures can be run and queries executed. Results are displayed in a grid, and can be pasted directly into a spreadsheet.
